// xBestIndex scan-hint flag bitmap — SQLITE_INDEX_SCAN_UNIQUE and friends.
// Spec §16.1.5 — vtab scan flags.
//
// Set by xBestIndex on sqlite3_index_info.idxFlags:
//   SQLITE_INDEX_SCAN_UNIQUE (0x01) — lookup returns at most 1 row
//   SQLITE_INDEX_SCAN_HEX    (0x02) — idxNum is hex-coded for display
// =============================================================================

